data.description: Welcome to your single-story retreat! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans 1638 sq ft with an open floor plan that welcomes you with abundant natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere throughout. The kitchen includes an island and separate dining space. The main suite offers a full bath, double vanity sink and oversized closet. Enjoy time outside on the covered patio and plenty of space on the .21 acre oversized lot. Conveniently located near Randolph AFB and the I35 Corridor. Walking distance to pool & just minutes to shopping & downtown Cibolo
